<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This book could have appeal for both. I work at a High-school Library and both students and staff loved this book. It is an eye opener regarding the m<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This book could have appeal for both. I work at a High-school Library and both students and staff loved this book. It is an eye opener regarding the mentality of young teens and the general naiveness of the parents. I would not want to be raising children, especially teens, with today's technology. This story is an eye opener!!<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
